title: Novikov 01 - 02 (2004) (Dragonz Onairam Choky Tanim) cbr
description:
An officer in the Imperial Police of St. Petersburg and in the service of Her Majesty Catherine II, tsarina of Russia, Alexis Novikov carries with him the tragedy of the death of his wife, the only case that he has never solved. He will stop at nothing to prevent further failures, and does not care if his methods do not appeal to his superiors.
